headline: Northern Trust Names Melanie Pickett to Lead Asset Servicing in the Americas
summary: CHICAGO, January 07, 2025--Melanie Pickett will oversee product and service delivery to asset manager clients as well as pensions, endowments, insurance and corporate clients.
